{
  "page": {
    "name": "服务参数编辑",
    "parent": "bot/energon/service_param/list",
    "type": 2,
    "sort": 11
  },
  "layout": {
    "type": "container",
    "children": {
      "page-main": {
        "type": "main",
        "className": "p-0",
        "children": {
          "dialog-shell": {
            "type": "container",
            "className": "w-full"
          }
        }
      }
    }
  },
  "nodes": {
    "dialog-shell": [
      {
        "id": "service-param-rule",
        "type": "form-radio",
        "value": "form.param_rule",
        "mode": "form",
        "option": "option.param_rule",
        "info": "直接映射：内部参数值直接写入字段标识；选项映射：参数选项转成来源字段值；附件映射：按序号取上传文件；组合映射：多个选项组合转字段值；固定值映射：直接写固定常量。",
        "meta": {
          "controlClassName": "min-w-[8rem]",
          "clearOnChange": [
            "form.param_id",
            "form.combo_param_ids",
            "form.mapping"
          ]
        }
      },
      {
        "id": "service-param-id",
        "type": "form-cascader",
        "value": "form.param_id",
        "mode": "form",
        "placeholder": "请选择参数",
        "info": "会按映射规则过滤：选项/组合只显示单选或多选参数，附件只显示文件参数，固定值不需要内部参数。",
        "meta": {
          "childParentField": "cate_id",
          "valueMode": "leaf",
          "placeholder": [
            "选择参数分类",
            "选择参数"
          ],
          "childExtraFields": "type,key,max_files",
          "clearOnChange": [
            "form.combo_param_ids",
            "form.combo_params",
            "form.mapping"
          ],
          "hiddenWhen": [
            {
              "path": "form.param_rule",
              "operator": "equals",
              "value": 5
            }
          ],
          "optionFilter": [
            {
              "field": "type",
              "path": "form.param_rule",
              "map": {
                "2": [
                  "option",
                  "multi_option"
                ],
                "3": [
                  "file",
                  "files"
                ],
                "4": [
                  "option",
                  "multi_option"
                ]
              }
            }
          ],
          "model": "bot.energon.NewParamCateModel",
          "childModel": "bot.energon.NewParamModel"
        }
      },
      {
        "id": "mapping-option",
        "type": "form-array",
        "name": "字段值",
        "value": "form.mapping",
        "mode": "form",
        "info": "不填来源字段值时，保存时会保留空值；调用时会回退使用内部选项值。",
        "meta": {
          "pageRoute": "/bot/energon/service_param/option_mapping",
          "addText": "添加字段值",
          "addAllText": "添加全部字段值",
          "clearText": "清空",
          "itemName": "字段值",
          "valueFormat": "json",
          "fillFromOption": {
            "optionKey": "mapping.option",
            "option": {
              "model": "bot.energon.NewParamOptionModel",
              "parentField": "param_id",
              "valueField": "id",
              "labelField": "name",
              "order": "sort asc,id asc",
              "pageSize": 200
            },
            "targetField": "option_id",
            "params": {
              "parentId": "form.param_id"
            },
            "defaultRow": {
              "native_value": ""
            }
          },
          "hiddenWhen": [
            {
              "path": "form.param_rule",
              "operator": "notEquals",
              "value": 2
            }
          ]
        }
      },
      {
        "id": "mapping-file",
        "type": "form-checkbox",
        "name": "字段值",
        "value": "form.mapping",
        "mode": "form",
        "option": {
          "service": "bot.energon.ParamOptionService.LoadFileIndexOptions",
          "valueField": "id",
          "labelField": "value"
        },
        "info": "选择要映射的文件序号。单文件参数只会使用第 1 个文件；多文件参数保存时会校验最大数量。",
        "meta": {
          "orientation": "horizontal",
          "optionParams": {
            "parentId": "form.param_id"
          },
          "hiddenCondition": "any",
          "hiddenWhen": [
            {
              "path": "form.param_rule",
              "operator": "notEquals",
              "value": 3
            },
            {
              "path": "form.param_id",
              "operator": "empty"
            }
          ]
        }
      },
      {
        "id": "mapping-combo-params",
        "type": "form-array",
        "name": "参与参数",
        "value": "form.combo_params",
        "mode": "form",
        "info": "组合映射的主参数是上方内部参数；这里添加额外参与参数。下方会按参与参数生成字段值表格。",
        "meta": {
          "pageRoute": "/bot/energon/service_param/combo_param",
          "addText": "添加参与参数",
          "clearText": "清空",
          "itemName": "参与参数",
          "clearOnChange": [
            "form.mapping"
          ],
          "fallbackRows": {
            "source": "form.mapping",
            "path": "params",
            "skipFirst": true,
            "targetField": "param_id"
          },
          "hiddenWhen": [
            {
              "path": "form.param_rule",
              "operator": "notEquals",
              "value": 4
            }
          ],
          "valueFormat": "json"
        }
      },
      {
        "id": "mapping-combo",
        "type": "form-combo-mapping",
        "name": "字段值",
        "value": "form.mapping",
        "mode": "form",
        "info": "按参与参数逐行选择参数选项，并填写组合后的来源字段值。",
        "meta": {
          "mainParamPath": "form.param_id",
          "extraParamsPath": "form.combo_params",
          "optionSourceKey": "combo.optionSource",
          "optionSourceOption": {
            "model": "bot.energon.NewParamOptionModel",
            "parentField": "param_id",
            "valueField": "id",
            "labelField": "name",
            "order": "sort asc,id asc",
            "pageSize": 200
          },
          "paramSourceKey": "combo.paramSource",
          "paramSourceOption": {
            "model": "bot.energon.NewParamModel",
            "valueField": "id",
            "labelField": "name",
            "pageSize": 200
          },
          "addText": "添加字段值",
          "addAllText": "添加全部字段值",
          "clearText": "清空",
          "hiddenWhen": [
            {
              "path": "form.param_rule",
              "operator": "notEquals",
              "value": 4
            }
          ]
        }
      },
      {
        "id": "mapping-fixed-type",
        "type": "form-radio",
        "name": "值类型",
        "value": "form.fixed_value_type",
        "mode": "form",
        "option": "option.fixed_value_type",
        "info": "固定值写入来源字段时使用的真实类型。布尔会写入 true/false，数字会写入 number，JSON 会写入对象或数组。",
        "meta": {
          "controlClassName": "min-w-[6rem]",
          "hiddenWhen": [
            {
              "path": "form.param_rule",
              "operator": "notEquals",
              "value": 5
            }
          ]
        }
      },
      {
        "id": "mapping-fixed",
        "type": "form-input",
        "name": "字段值",
        "value": "form.mapping",
        "mode": "form",
        "placeholder": "例如：false、123、{\"enabled\":true}",
        "info": "固定值不读取内部参数，会按值类型写入字段标识对应的来源字段。",
        "meta": {
          "controlClassName": "min-w-[16rem]",
          "hiddenWhen": [
            {
              "path": "form.param_rule",
              "operator": "notEquals",
              "value": 5
            }
          ]
        }
      },
      {
        "type": "form-input",
        "value": "form.key",
        "mode": "form",
        "info": "不填则使用内部参数的标识。支持对象/数组路径，例如 content[1].image_url.url。ComfyUI 工作流需要加上节点ID，比如 10.text。",
        "meta": {
          "controlClassName": "min-w-[10rem]"
        }
      },
      {
        "type": "form-input",
        "name": "字段名",
        "value": "form.name",
        "mode": "form",
        "placeholder": "例如：超级提示词",
        "info": "可选展示名。普通映射不填时展示内部参数名；固定值映射没有内部参数，不填则留空。填写后只影响后台展示。",
        "meta": {
          "controlClassName": "min-w-[10rem]"
        }
      }
    ]
  },
  "data": {
    "form": {
      "param_rule": 1,
      "fixed_value_type": "string",
      "mapping": ""
    },
    "option": {
      "param_rule": [
        {
          "id": 1,
          "value": "直接映射"
        },
        {
          "id": 2,
          "value": "选项映射"
        },
        {
          "id": 3,
          "value": "附件映射"
        },
        {
          "id": 4,
          "value": "组合映射"
        },
        {
          "id": 5,
          "value": "固定值映射"
        }
      ],
      "fixed_value_type": [
        {
          "id": "string",
          "value": "字符串"
        },
        {
          "id": "boolean",
          "value": "布尔"
        },
        {
          "id": "number",
          "value": "数字"
        },
        {
          "id": "json",
          "value": "JSON"
        }
      ]
    }
  },
  "state": {},
  "action": {
    "submit": {
      "type": "save",
      "params": "form"
    }
  }
}
